This pain ain’t no joke!! I promise y’all I’m dizzy done having babies lol!! 
So what I’m dealing with right now, is trapped gas which is very common after surgery! I’m drinking plenty of water 💦 and also taking my walks. The pain medicine works wonders but once it kicks out my system I could cry a whole River. It’s so nice having my baby girl here. She is absolutely beautiful. I cant wait to share more content of her with you guys. 🫶🏽🤍 until then I am trying to recover and get better so I can take care of my other babies. Mom of three now! Let’s just say 😮‍💨 bc having a baby in my 30s was so much more difficult on my body than it was in my early 20’s but I do thank God for a healthy delivery, and a healthy baby girl. 🫶🏽 and I pray he continues to keep his arms wrapped us and keep us safe in this healing process. 
.
.
Also, if y’all have any tips for c sections mommas drop them in the comment below ? Bc Id love to learn about something I don’t know, and we could be helping someone else as well, thank you 😊
